<div class="title">Nirvana, or Just a Scrambled Brain?</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B, Blue Lotus & Salvia divinorum</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Ray+Aten&Exact=1">Ray Aten</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Ray Aten. "Nirvana, or Just a Scrambled Brain?: An Experience with 2C-B, Blue Lotus & Salvia divinorum (exp3040)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 8, 2000. erowid.org/exp/3040</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
